### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiKey = your-api-key

### Ingest Reviews
POST {{baseUrl}}/ingest
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

[
  {
    "location": "Bangalore",
    "rating": 5,
    "text": "Amazing food and service!",
    "date": "2025-10-07"
  },
  {
    "location": "Delhi",
    "rating": 2,
    "text": "Very slow delivery and bad taste.",
    "date": "2025-10-06"
  }
]

### Get All Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews?page=1&pagesize=10

### Get Reviews by Location
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews?location=Bangalore

### Get Reviews by Sentiment
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews?sentiment=POSITIVE

### Search Similar Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=great+service&k=3

### Get Review by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/1

### Suggest AI Reply for a Review
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews/1/suggest-reply
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Analytics Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics
